Troubleshooting¶

PygraphViz¶

If you have difficulty installing PygraphViz, try to install GraphViz first. For Mac this would be:

brew install graphviz
python -m pip install pygraphviz

If that doesn’t work, try also:

brew doctor
brew install graphviz
python -m pip install pygraphviz
